*libfwbuilder-1.0.1-r1 (13 Nov 2003)

  13 Nov 2003; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> libfwbuilder-1.0.1-r1.ebuild :
  Added patch from upstream CVS. When built against libxml2 2.6.2 fwbuilder would exit with an 
  error. See upstream #840427.

